        "version_name": "和合本新標點（神版）",
        "lang": "cht",
        "text": "神又說：『使他們作奴僕的那國，我要懲罰。以後他們要出來，在這地方事奉我。』"
      },
      "nasb": {
        "version_id": "NASB",
        "version_name": "New American Standard Bible",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "‘And whatever nation to which they will be in bondage I Myself will judge,’ said God, ‘and after that they will come out and  serve Me in this place.’"
      },
      "niv": {
        "version_id": "NIV",
        "version_name": "New International Version",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "But I will punish the nation they serve as slaves,’ God said, ‘and afterward they will come out of that country and worship me in this place.’"
      },
      "nlt": {
        "version_id": "NLT",
        "version_name": "New Living Translation",
        "lang": "en",
        "text": "‘But I will punish the nation that enslaves them,’ God said, ‘and in the end they will come out and worship me here in this place.’"
      }
